  "1423630": {
    "name": "Holiday Harry",
    "steam_appid": 1423630,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎄 Holiday horror comes home... and it's sitting right above your fireplace. 🎄</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1423630/extras/78fe43d6e9a19a1dcded41223a474c98.poster.avif?t=1766520008\" width=630 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1423630/extras/78fe43d6e9a19a1dcded41223a474c98.webm?t=1766520008\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1423630/extras/78fe43d6e9a19a1dcded41223a474c98.mp4?t=1766520008\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Holiday Harry</strong> is an homage to killer doll slashers and classic holiday horror films. 🔪</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A<strong> </strong>short, tense thriller adventure   experience designed to be completed in one sitting. Perfect for fans of old-school holiday horror.  Play as <strong>Alex</strong>, returning to the snowy home she grew up in, only to be pulled into a winter nightmare she’ll never forget.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the house, prepare for a Christmas get-together, and uncover the terror waiting above the fireplace.<br>Inspired by late-90s classics, <strong>Holiday Harry</strong> combines third-person gameplay with retro fixed-camera angles, low-poly visuals, optional VHS-style filters, and a nostalgic 4:3 aspect ratio.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1423630/extras/082bf4d1e1e2ab54c1fe71f247c7c817.poster.avif?t=1766520008\" width=630 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1423630/extras/082bf4d1e1e2ab54c1fe71f247c7c817.webm?t=1766520008\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1423630/extras/082bf4d1e1e2ab54c1fe71f247c7c817.mp4?t=1766520008\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Alex inherits her grandmother's house after her passing and decides to throw a Christmas party for her friends. However, Holiday Harry has party plans of his own...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survive a night of terror—and try to defeat Holiday Harry, if you can...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1423630/extras/f8ccadf7c27a5abad992f1b4a0047c57.poster.avif?t=1766520008\" width=630 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1423630/extras/f8ccadf7c27a5abad992f1b4a0047c57.webm?t=1766520008\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1423630/extras/f8ccadf7c27a5abad992f1b4a0047c57.mp4?t=1766520008\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Game Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Full Controller support / Universal Controller support - Works with most gamepads including third-party ones such as 8BitDo controllers.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >PSX-inspired, wobbly, mind-boggling graphics!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Retro 4:3 aspect ratio with a low resolution of 960x720.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Optional VHS and CRT retro filters that can be toggled on or off.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >90s nostalgia, twinkling Christmas lights, and a killer doll on the loose...</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1423630/extras/55dac026e29b2d3e35e55243c4b523e0.poster.avif?t=1766520008\" width=630 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1423630/extras/55dac026e29b2d3e35e55243c4b523e0.webm?t=1766520008\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1423630/extras/55dac026e29b2d3e35e55243c4b523e0.mp4?t=1766520008\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Toggle VHS and CRT filters on or off to capture that nostalgic 90s vibe! 📺</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can easily access them from the pause menu or quickly cycle through them with a single press of the Select button on your controller or the F key on your keyboard.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1423630/extras/4471e697780ff9effa47efa827ae5225.poster.avif?t=1766520008\" width=480 height=358 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1423630/extras/4471e697780ff9effa47efa827ae5225.webm?t=1766520008\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1423630/extras/4471e697780ff9effa47efa827ae5225.mp4?t=1766520008\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Featuring a new second game mode. Play as Holiday Harry and punish them all in Christmas Nightmare!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1423630/extras/d1a2fd1f9f643d7b09f6a3a1e3f377a2.poster.avif?t=1766520008\" width=1024 height=1024 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1423630/extras/d1a2fd1f9f643d7b09f6a3a1e3f377a2.webm?t=1766520008\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1423630/extras/d1a2fd1f9f643d7b09f6a3a1e3f377a2.mp4?t=1766520008\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1423630/extras/0222b094d04db3ac437bc21d7ffea01d.poster.avif?t=1766520008\" width=600 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1423630/extras/0222b094d04db3ac437bc21d7ffea01d.webm?t=1766520008\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1423630/extras/0222b094d04db3ac437bc21d7ffea01d.mp4?t=1766520008\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Look for the “Samer Khatib Official Seal Of Quality™” in our works!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1423630/extras/03ed977476ccfef196e6a3da22358234.poster.avif?t=1766520008\" width=600 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1423630/extras/03ed977476ccfef196e6a3da22358234.webm?t=1766520008\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1423630/extras/03ed977476ccfef196e6a3da22358234.mp4?t=1766520008\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>✨ Made with love, passion and, magic. ✨</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Be sure to check out more Samer Khatib games. Now playing at a game store near you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1423630/extras/1dbc2a99fd82ec5f11d2fd65647df203.poster.avif?t=1766520008\" width=600 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1423630/extras/1dbc2a99fd82ec5f11d2fd65647df203.webm?t=1766520008\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1423630/extras/bd4ef2d29c8743265964fdcef89278b4.poster.avif?t=1766520008\" width=300 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1423630/extras/bd4ef2d29c8743265964fdcef89278b4.webm?t=1766520008\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1423630/extras/bd4ef2d29c8743265964fdcef89278b4.mp4?t=1766520008\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1423630/extras/983b34da220094ba5b7c5720e3343799.poster.avif?t=1766520008\" width=300 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1423630/extras/983b34da220094ba5b7c5720e3343799